descriptionHtml:
Hi Guys,

This is yet another playerhouse near Anisa`s Cabin , I made this for personal use but I thought maybe other people would like to try it out too :) .

All of the creating tools are outside the house and a alchemy desk inside the house.
your companions can`t enter the house, need to learn how to make them able to enter the house with you.

this is my first mod for skyrim so be gentle to me :P.


enjoy the mod and I hope you like it

Update: I have add some environment changes ,like water and waterfalls I hope you like it ! :)
Update 2: your followers can get inside the house 
Update 3: removed stairs outside and made a underground location, you can go there from inside of house by entering the first floor of the house and on the left side there is the entrance located on the ground :) 


Outside the house you will find the following:

-A forge
-Smelter
-Grinder
-Cooking spot
-A garden with flowers and bees flying around
-A some vegetation ( just next to the flowers )

Inside the house there is a Alchemy table.

I have added all of this stuff because this was made for personal use at first but I thought maybe others would enjoy it too :)



the area is tweaked alot so if there is a another mod using the same cells then the gam emight crash or other weird things could happen :)
author: Isa Khan
